Caroline Blakiston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caroline_Blakiston 0 Caroline Blakiston (born 13 February 1933) is an English actress. She is best known in her native United Kingdom for her role in the television comedy series Brass, and to international audiences as Mon Mothma in the Star Wars film Return of the Jedi.
